# Files Claude Code should exclude from its file index.
# Keep this list narrow — only files that are actively noisy or never
# relevant to code work belong here. See CLAUDE.md for what each script does.

# Root-level user-facing docs — pure pitch/hub content, repeated in the root
# CLAUDE.md, not implementation. Anchored with a leading "/" so this does NOT
# match platforms/*/README.md — those carry real per-platform env-var/usage
# spec content that IS relevant when working inside a platform folder.
/LICENSE
/README.md

# Non-functional repo metadata
.github/FUNDING.yml
.github/dependabot.yml

# Tooling output / local-only state (also gitignored)
semgrep-findings.json
.claude/
node_modules/
dist/
